インタフェース QuoteByDestinationAmountRequest

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    InterledgerPacket, QuoteRequest

    public interface QuoteByDestinationAmountRequest
extends QuoteRequest
    A request for a quote that specifies the amount to deliver at the destination address.
